HEADWORD: Brindled
<hw>Brin"dled</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[A dim. form of
<ets>brinded</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having dark streaks or spots on a gray
or tawny ground; brinded.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧With a <xex>brindled</xex> lion
played.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Churchill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
